rComments: The only class that matters at the end of my 4 years at U of T. This class will unfortunately not be taught anymore.
This course was the highlight of my four years at U of T. If this course is still offered and taught by Satchu I would do whatever I could to enrol - you won't be dissapointed.

Hands down - the best class at U of T. This is an opportunity for which one would pay many thousands of dollars outside university. Be respectful, come ready for class, participate and get the chance of a lifetime. If you don't plan to work and think hard then don't bother enrolling. Otherwise, take the course - it WILL change the way you think!
